INSERT INTO `laptops` VALUES ('10550143','Acer Aspire ES 17.3\" Laptop - Black','499.99','Stay efficient in everyday computing with the Acer Aspire ES1-732-P54M 17.3\" laptop. Powered by an Intel Pentium quad-core processor and 4GB RAM, this laptop is best for everyday activities like surfing the web, word processing, and light multitasking. HDMI connectivity lets you connect to an external display, while the Precision Touchpad ensures smooth navigation.','<ul><li>1.1GHz Intel Pentium N4200 quad core processor and 4GB RAM power reliable performance for everyday computing tasks</li><li>500GB hard drive provides ample storage space for your documents, photos, music, videos, movies, and other miscellaneous files</li><li>17.3-inch LCD display with a resolution of 1600 x 900 gives you lots of screen real estate that presents content in bright and clear detail</li><li>802.11b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi makes it easy to connect to wireless networks at home, at the office, or at a coffee shop when you\'re on the go</li><li>Integrated Ethernet port lets you connect directly to your home or office\'s internet network for faster and more reliable connection speeds</li><li>Connectivity options include Bluetooth, a USB 3.0 port, and a pair of USB 2.0 ports so you can easily connect peripherals such as a printer or external hard drive</li><li>HDMI output lets you connect to a secondary display, including HDTVs and HD monitors, so you can work on a larger screen</li><li>Acer\'s Precision Touchpad makes touch control as precise and gestures as smooth as on a touchscreen, with support for Windows 10 features</li><li>M-DISC Ready drive allows you to archive content onto M-DISCs, ideal for backing up files like photographs</li><li>Preinstalled with Windows 10 Home operating system, which features a refined internet browser, improved Start menu, digital assistant with Cortana, universal Windows apps, and much more</li></ul>'),('11664920','ASUS ZenBook 14\" Laptop - Quartz Grey','899.99','Stay productive and creative anywhere you go with this ASUS 14\" ZenBook UX430UA laptop, which features a brilliant Full HD 1080p NanoEdge bezel display, Intel Core i3 processor, 8GB of RAM, and a 128GB solid state drive. Built-in Wi-Fi and integrated Bluetooth add wireless connectivity, while a micro HDMI output lets you connect to a secondary HD display.','<ul><li>2.4GHz Intel Core i3-7100U processer and 8GB of DDR3 RAM deliver solid and reliable performance for effortless everyday computing and more</li><li>128GB solid state drive loads files quickly and has fewer moving parts than a traditional hard disc, minimizing the risk of malfunction</li><li>14-inch wide-view NanoEdge bezel display with a native resolution of 1920 x 1080 presents images, videos, apps, software, and other content in crisp, crystal-clear detail</li><li>802.11ac Wi-Fi gives you the freedom to connect to wireless networks at home, at the office, or to hotspots when you\'re on the go</li><li>Bluetooth functionality allows you to wirelessly connect a range of compatible devices, such as a gaming headset or external speakers</li><li>Total of 3 USB ports (1 x USB 3.1 Type C, 1 x USB 3.0, and 1 x USB 2.0) make it easy to expand functionality by connecting a range of peripherals, such as a printer, keyboard, and mouse</li><li>Micro HDMI output lets you connect the laptop to an HD monitor or HDTV for use as a secondary display</li><li>Preinstalled with Windows 10 operating system, which features a refined internet browser, improved Start menu, digital assistant with Cortana, universal Windows apps, and much more</li><li>Built-in fingerprint reader offers secure 1-touch login via Windows Hello feature</li></ul>'),('11797035','ASUS ROG GL503VM 15.6\" - Dragon Scale','1,912.98','Get a leg up on the competition with this ASUS ROG GL503VM gaming laptop. Featuring 16GB of RAM and a GeForce GTX 1060 graphics card with 6GB of dedicated video memory, this laptop lets you play your favourite games at their highest settings. It\'s also packing Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, HDMI output, and a hybrid drive with 1TB of SHDD capacity and 256GB of SSD storage.','<ul><li>2.8GHz Intel Core i7-7700HQ quad-core processor and 16GB of RAM provide speedy and reliable computing power to deliver premium gaming experiences</li><li>Hybrid drive with 1TB of SSHD capacity and 256GB of SSD storage offers the best of both worlds, combining the large capacity of a hard disc drive with the fast performance of a solid state drive</li><li>NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 graphics card with 6GB of video memory supports 4K Ultra HD visuals and VR experiences, with professional-grade performance so you can play games at their highest settings </li><li>15.6-inch Full HD display with a native resolution of 1920 x 1080 presents images, videos, apps, software, and other content in crisp, crystal-clear detail</li><li>802.11a/c Wi-Fi makes it easy to connect to your home network from the couch or the dinner table, or to any Wi-Fi hotspot</li><li>Integrated Bluetooth and 5 USB ports (4 x USB 3.0 and 1 x USB 3.1 Type C Gen 1) and a headphone-out/audio-in combo jack, and a RJ45 LAN jack let you easily connect a range of additional peripherals, such as a printer or wireless headphones</li><li>HDMI and Mini DisplayPort output give you the option of hooking your laptop up to an HDTV or HD monitor for use as a secondary display </li><li>Preinstalled with Windows 10 Home operating system, which features a refined internet browser, improved Start menu, digital assistant with Cortana, universal Windows apps, and much more</li></ul>'),('12309813','Microsoft Surface Book 2 15\" 2-in-1','4,199.99','Powerhouse performance, incredible graphics, and a versatile multi-mode design make the Microsoft Surface Book 2 a remarkably robust laptop, tablet, and portable studio all in one. It offers up to 17 hours of battery life, twice the power of its predecessor, and a brilliant PixelSense display. Connectivity options include AC Wi-Fi, two USB 3.1 ports, and a USB-C port.','<ul><li>4.2GHz 8th Gen Intel Core i7-8650U processor and 16GB of RAM offer twice the power of the previous model, making this the fastest Surface Book yet</li><li>1000GB solid state drive ensures you enjoy fast loading applications and quick access to all your important files</li><li>15-inch vibrant PixelSense touchscreen display with an outstanding 3240 x 2160 resolution </li><li>NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 discrete GPU with 6GB VRAM generates great-looking visuals</li><li>The 10-point multi-touch G5 touchscreen provides an intuitive way to interact with your applications</li><li>Built-in 802.11ac Wi-Fi allows you to connect wirelessly to your home network or any public Wi-Fi hotspot, while integrated Bluetooth 4.1 lets you easily pair with your Bluetooth-enabled devices</li><li>Memory card reader supports SDXC UHS-II cards up to 128GB</li><li>Get up to 17 hours of battery life for video playback (with base) to keep you productive and entertained all day long (5 hours without the base connected)</li><li>Four versatile modes of use: laptop, tablet, studio, and view</li><li>USB-C port offers fast data transfer speeds and the convenience of a reversible design</li><li>Two USB 3.1 ports, a full-size SD card reader, and 2 Surface Connect ports let you connect and expand</li><li>Full HD 1080p front and rear cameras let you take highly detailed photos and enjoy lifelike video calls</li><li>Pre-loaded with Windows 10 Pro Creators Update 64-bit</li></ul>'),('12388676','Dell Inspiron 15.6\" Laptop - Platinum Silver','1,099.99','The Dell Inspiron 15.6\" Laptop features an elegant, thin-bezel design that gives you added screen space for whatever media you are viewing or any documents on which you are working. A speedy processor, generous amount of memory, tons of RAM, and SmartByte technology mean that this laptop is doing everything it can to work for you.','<ul><li>1.8GHz Intel i7-8550U quad- processor gives you reliable speed and performance </li><li>Elegant thin-bezel design on this 15.6\" laptop gives you added screen space for gorgeous visuals</li><li>Screen has a native resolution of 1920 x 1080 for crisp images and clear graphics</li><li>FHD HD IPS display lets you view your screen from a wide range of angles without sacrificing image quality</li><li>Waves MaxxAudio Pro delivers professional-grade sound, immersing you in clear highs and enhanced bass</li><li>SmartByte technology enables a superior streaming experience</li><li>1TB HDD memory and 128GB SSD provides plenty of space for all your precious memories</li><li>Hybrid storage system makes everything you do faster, smoother, and easier</li><li>8GB DDR4 RAM lets you run complex programs with ease</li><li>NVIDIA GeForce MX130 graphics with 4GB GDDR5 memory delivers top speed with no lag time</li><li>180-degree hinge lets you lay your screen flat for easier collaboration</li><li>Built-in infrared camera works with Windows Hello for secure facial recognition, keeping your laptop secure</li><li>USB 3.1 Type-C port allows for universal charging</li><li>HDMI 2.0 port allows videos to be played on an external 4K UHD display</li><li>Backlit keyboard allows you to work in dim light settings</li><li>Windows 10 operating system for quick and intuitive use</li></ul>'),('12567415','HP ENVY 17.3\" Touchscreen Laptop - Silver','1,499.99','Enjoy robust multitasking performance with this 17.3” HP laptop, which features a 1.8GHz Intel Core i7 processor, 12GB of DDR4 RAM, and a massive 1TB hard drive for all your storage needs. It also features integrated Bluetooth and 4 USB ports so you can connect a wide range of additional peripherals.','<ul><li>1.8 GHz 8th Generation Intel Core i7-8550U quad-core processor and 12GB of DDR4-2400 power solid and reliable performance for all of your everyday computing needs</li><li>1TB hard drive offers tons of storage space so you can keep all of your documents and media files just a quick click away </li><li>17.3-inch Full HD touchscreen display with a native resolution of 1920 x 1080 presents images, videos, apps, software, and other content in crisp, crystal-clear detail</li><li>802.11b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi gives you a fast wireless connection to your home or office Wi-Fi network, or to hotspots around town</li><li>10/100/1000 GbE LAN Ethernet port gives you the option of connecting to your network with a secure and reliable wired connection for potentially faster download and upload speeds</li><li>Integrated Bluetooth and 4 USB ports let you easily connect a range of additional peripherals, such as a printer or wireless headphones</li><li>HDMI and Mini DisplayPort output give you the option of hooking your laptop up to an HDTV or HD monitor for use as a secondary display </li></ul>'),('12619439','Dell XPS 13.3\" Laptop - Rose Gold/White','1,799.99','Slim, strong, and boasting ultra-long battery life, Dell\'s XPS 13.3\" laptop packs an 8th generation Intel Core i7 processor for maximum performance and a 256GB solid state drive for ample storage with fast boot times. It comes with a stunningly detailed InfinityEdge 13.3\" Full HD display.','<ul><li>4GHz 8th generation Intel Core i7-8550U quad-core processor and 8GB of DDR4 RAM combine to deliver blazing speeds for avid multitaskers and power users </li><li>Dynamic Power Mode squeezes every drop of power out of the CPU, pushing your 15W processor up to 23W when you need it</li><li>256GB solid state drive provides a fast response with quick startup times as well as ample storage for your music, photos, and applications</li><li>Intel UHD Graphics 620 uses shared video memory with low power consumption, so you can enjoy watching movies and viewing photos without taxing your system</li><li>13.3\" anti-glare IPS display with a 1920 x 1080 native resolution boasts a 1500:1 contrast ratio and maximizes the colour spectrum with 100% sRGB colour for the sharpest, brightest picture quality</li><li>InfinityEdge display offers an impressive 80.7% screen-to-body ratio</li><li>Integrated Bluetooth 4.1 allows you to wirelessly connect a range of compatible devices, such as a gaming headset or external speakers</li><li>Integrated 802.11ac Wi-Fi support provides faster speeds and wider coverage, and is backwards compatible with other hotspots and Wi-Fi networks</li><li>52Wh lithium-ion battery provides up to 19 hours of power for all-day use</li><li>3 x USB-C ports (2 of which are Thunderbolt 3 compatible) for connecting 4K external monitors, peripherals, and enjoying fast data transfers up to an impressive 40GB per second</li><li>At 2.67lb., the 13.3\" XPS is a lightweight computer you can take with you wherever you go</li><li>Built-in micro-SD card reader makes it easier to quickly transfer files from your SD card to your laptop</li><li>Premium unibody design with an inlayed stainless-steel logo and laser-etched details is cut from a single block of aluminum for a more durable frame, and the Corning Gorilla Glass 4 screen provides superior damage resistance </li><li>Built with GORE Thermal Insulation to keep your computer running at low temperatures so it won\'t overheat even during extended use</li><li>Dell Mobile Connect easily connects your smartphone to your computer and offers features like forwarding notifications to your computer screen so you can limit distractions while working, and secure connections over unsecure networks</li><li>Built-in webcam lets you video chat with friends, family and work</li><li>Pre-installed with Windows 10 Home operating system, which features a refined internet browser, improved Start menu, digital assistant with Cortana, universal Windows apps, and much more </li></ul>'),('12620841','HP OMEN 15.6\" Gaming Laptop','1,799.99','Give your gaming the competitive edge of the HP OMEN 15.6\" laptop with its overly ample 1TB and 128GB SSD storage. It features a powerful Intel Core i7-8750H processor with 16GB RAM to effortlessly handle multitasking, streaming movies, video and photo editing, and smooth, blur-free gaming action enhanced with the NVIDIA GeForce GTX graphics card.','<ul><li>2.2GHz 8th gen Intel Core i7-8750H processor with 16GB of RAM delivers smooth multitasking and powerful performance for streaming movies, playing intensive games, and editing videos or photos</li><li>1TB 7200 RPM SATA hard drive offers a compact digital warehouse so you can reliably store all your documents, movies, music, photos, and other media files in one place</li><li>128GB PCIe NVMe M.2 solid state drive helps optimize your computer\'s performance by delivering quick boot-up and load times, not to mention fast access to your frequently used files</li><li>15.6\" diagonal FHD(39) WLED-backlit display with 1920 x 1080 resolution features colour-popping IPS technology, an anti-glare screen, and a thin micro-edge for ultra-wide viewing angles</li><li>NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 graphics card with 6GB GDDR5 dedicated video memory enables smooth, blur-free gaming</li><li>Built-in 802.11b/g/n/ac (2x2) Wi-Fi and Bluetooth 4.2 combo (MU-MIMO supported) provides fast, seamless connections to your wireless networks and improved coverage for distance and range</li><li>Integrated Bluetooth 4.2 lets you pair with compatible Bluetooth-enabled devices like smartphones, printers, and speakers for a convenient wireless experience</li><li>3 USB 3.1 Gen 1 ports, 1 Thunderbolt 3 port, 1 mini display port, 1 RJ-45 port, 1 headphone/microphone combo (DTS headphone: X enabled), and 1 microphone input jack allow you to plug in a range of peripherals, including thumb drives, headsets, and more</li><li>HDMI 2.0 connectivity lets you connect to an HD monitor or HDTV, giving your games and movies big screen viewing</li><li>Dual speakers with audio by Bang and Olufsen supports DTS Headphone: X and produces exceptional sound for an immersive experience</li><li>Multi-format digital media card reader lets you effortlessly transfer videos and photos from your media cards onto your laptop for viewing and editing</li><li>Front-facing HP Wide Vision HD Webcam with integrated dual array digital microphones let you challenge and chat with friends and competitors while gaming or video chat with your family</li><li>Full-size 4-zone lighting backlit keyboard with numeric keypad and NKRO provide comfort and efficiency during use</li><li>Preloaded with Windows 10 Home, which features a refined browser for surfing the web, improved Start menu, Cortana digital assistant, Windows apps, and so much more</li></ul>'),('12650346','Dell XPS 13.3\" Touchscreen Laptop - Silver','2,399.99','This Dell XPS laptop is a powerhouse you can stow in your briefcase or backpack. It packs an 8th Generation Intel Core processor and 16GB of RAM to effortlessly handle the demands of your resource-intensive applications. This exceptionally slim and lightweight machine also boasts a stunning 4K InfinityEdge touch display and 512GB solid state drive.','<ul><li>1.8GHz 8th generation Intel Core i7-8550U processor with 16GB of RAM provides high-efficiency power and premium performance for multitaskers and heavy users</li><li>Dynamic Power Mode squeezes every ounce of power the CPU has to give when you need it</li><li>512GB solid state drive provides a fast response with quick startup times as well as ample storage for your music, photos, and applications </li><li>Intel UHD Graphics 620 uses shared video memory with low power consumption, so you can enjoy watching movies and playing games without taxing your system</li><li>13.3\" anti-glare IPS touch-enabled display with a 3840 x 2160 &nbsp;native resolution boasts a 1500:1 contrast ratio and maximizes the colour spectrum with 100% sRGB colour for the sharpest, brightest picture quality</li><li>InfinityEdge display provides an 80.7% screen-to-body ratio so you can enjoy less bezel and more 4K visuals</li><li>Corning Gorilla Glass 4 screen provides superior damage resistance </li><li>Integrated Bluetooth 4.1 allows you to wirelessly connect a range of compatible devices, such as a gaming headset or external speakers</li><li>Integrated 802.11ac Wi-Fi support provides faster speeds and wider coverage, and is backwards compatible with other hotspots and Wi-Fi networks</li><li>ENERGY STAR Certified laptop uses a 52WH lithium battery that provides extra-long battery life of up to 19 hours</li><li>At 2.67lb., this laptop is designed to let you keep powerhouse performance with you for wherever you want to sign in and work</li><li>Comes with 2 Thunderbolt 3 ports with PowerShare, and a DisplayPort for connecting 4K external monitors and enjoying fast data transfers</li><li>1 x USB 3.1 port and 1 x 3.1 USB Type-C port for connecting peripherals and accessories like a printer, mouse, or even your smartphone</li><li>Built-in micro-SD card reader makes it easier to quickly transfer files from your camera</li><li>Premium unibody design with an inlayed stainless-steel logo and laser-etched details is cut from a single block of aluminum for an incredibly durable frame</li><li>Built with GORE Thermal Insulation to keep your computer running stably at low temperatures </li><li>Preloaded with Windows 10 Home operating system, which features a refined internet browser, improved Start menu, digital assistant with Cortana, universal Windows apps, and much more</li></ul>'),('12727801','Apple MacBook Pro with Touch Bar 15.4\"','3,699.99','The new MacBook Pro has 6-core Intel Core processors for up to 70 percent faster compute speeds.1 A brilliant and colourful Retina display featuring True Tone technology for a more true-to-life viewing experience. And the versatile Touch Bar for more ways to be productive. It’s Apple’s most powerful notebook. Pushed even further.','<ul><li>6-core Intel Core i7 processor</li><li>Brilliant Retina display with True Tone technology</li><li>Touch Bar and Touch ID </li><li>Radeon Pro 560X graphics with 4GB of video memory</li><li>Intel UHD Graphics 630 </li><li>Ultrafast SSD</li><li>Four Thunderbolt 3 (USB-C) ports </li><li>Up